snippet.title: ESBC Official Alpha Gameplay Features (First Look)
snippet.description:
Check out the new video showing an overview of the fight mechanics and some Career Mode info in ESBC.

Check out our full game roster, including plenty of other boxing greats including Joe Louis, Julio Cesar Chavez, and Sugar Ray Leonard, here: https://www.esportsboxingclub.com/roster/
